alert.note: Alert for Los Angeles County Mountains; Santa Monica Mountains (California) Issued by the National Weather Service

info.headline: High Wind Warning issued January 26 at 2:08PM PST until January 26 at 10:00PM PST by NWS Oxnard
info.description: ...HIGH WIND WARNING REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 10 PM PST THIS EVENING... * WHAT...Northeast winds 35 to 45 mph with gusts up to 70 mph expected. * WHERE...Los Angeles County Mountains and Santa Monica Mountains. * WHEN...Until 10 PM PST this evening. * IMPACTS...Damaging winds will blow down large objects such as trees and power lines. Power outages are expected. Travel will be difficult, especially for high profile vehicles.
info.instruction: People should avoid being outside in forested areas and around trees and branches. If possible, remain in the lower levels of your home during the windstorm, and avoid windows. Use caution if you must drive.
